com.centurylink.mdw.startup

Interface StartupClass

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    StartupService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CacheRegistration, ConnectionPoolRegistration, FileListenerRegistration, MdwWebSocketServer, TimerTaskRegistration

    public interface StartupClass
    The interface needs to be implemented if it is desired that the class is loaded and executed when the server is started The framework will load this class and execute the onStartup method at start up.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onShutdown()
      Method that gets invoked when the server shuts down
      void onStartup()
      Method that gets invoked when the server comes up The impl class will have logic to that gets executed when the server starts up
